						<summary>

						<p>This is built in at the end. It seems to record some provision made by a resident of Tiruvēṭpūr for the celebration of a festival on the day of asterism Uttiram in Paṅguṉi month to god Gaṇapati in the temple at Śrī-Gōkarṇam in Kavira-nāḍu. (No. 54 of <hi rend="italic">Pud. Ins.</hi> Texts).</p>						

